title: Bonus Episode! - Buried Treasure of Skate Punk w/ Shane Told (Silverstein, Lead Singer Syndrome podcast)
itunes:title: Bonus Episode! - Buried Treasure of Skate Punk w/ Shane Told (Silverstein, Lead Singer Syndrome podcast)
description:
BONUS EPISODE! - Skate Punk Buried Treasure w/ Shane Told (Silverstein, Lead Singer Syndrome podcast): Surprise, here is a rad chat that I had with my good friend and fellow podcaster, Shane Told, about the beauty that is skate punk and some bands that are often overlooked in the genera. Hope you find some undiscovered gems in here! Bands/Songs played in the episodeMillencolin - “No Cigar”Diesel Boy - “Titty Twister”Guns N Wankers “Skin Deep”Bigwig - “Dent”Hi Standard “California Dreaming”Rufio - “In My Eyes”Straight Faced “Show Me Your Gun”Donuts N Glory

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
